  <div id="tplPage" class="wspUi"><div id="tplTitle"><div id="tplTitleLogo"><img src="../res/logoOpale3.png" alt width="48" height="48"></div><span id="tplTitleMain">Welcome to Opale 3.5</span><span id="tplTitlesub">Pedagogical content creation</span></div><div id="tplTabs"><div id="tplTabCo"><div id="tplTabCoScroll"><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti"><span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale 3.5</span></h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p "><span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale 3.5</span>  is a publishing chain for the production of academic training documents that can be used for on-site training, distance or blended learning. Opale provides solutions for  educational contents management and multi-format publications:</p><ul class="txt_sl "><li class="txt_m "><span>paper-based documents (OpenDocument and PDF formats),</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>slideshow,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>web site,</span></li><li class="txt_m "><span>SCORM 1.2 and 2004 modules that can be integrated into a LMS platform.</span></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="infoblock"><h1 class="infoblock_ti">One application, two versions</h1><div class="infoblock_co"><div class="text "><p class="txt_p ">Two versions of <span class="txt_vName_el ">Opale 3.5</span> exist in order to answer various needs:</p><ul class="txt_il "><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p "><strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">Opale Starter</strong>, designed for trainers and teachers wishing to autonomously produce their training modules without needing any specific training;</p></li><li class="txt_ili "><p class="txt_p "><strong class="txt_emphasis_is ">Opale</strong>, designed for trainers and teachers with advanced production, content management, re-usability or indexation needs.</p><p class="txt_p ">This publishing chain is also designed for organizations, training centers and schools needing solutions for managing the production and the publishing of advanced academic training documents.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div id="tplTabBar"><span class=" tabSel_yes"><span>Presentation</span></span><a href="welcome.html" target="_self" class=" tabSel_no"><span>About...</span></a></div></div></div>
